The Chaos Juggler is responsible for providing top-notch administrative support to our CEO and senior leadership team. The ideal candidate will possess people skills that are way beyond average and have an attitude and personality that makes them suited to work in a fast paced environment with a very busy executive. The Chaos Juggler will work primarily from our location in downtown Austin, and in addition to assisting our CEO and senior leadership team, will handle the day to day running of our office.</p>
<p>
<strong>YOU:</strong><br />
Can multitask; are capable of making smart and timely decisions with limited guidance; love details; can problem solve and find answers as needed; anticipate needs rather than just meeting them; like to work with a team to ensure things get done, work efficiently on your own, don&rsquo;t mind helping out other team members, are humble, probably a little quirky, and like to help people, period.<br />
